---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resume — Mas Muhammad" description="Download or print the resume of Mas Muhammad, Senior Backend Engineer with 11 years of experience in .NET, distributed systems, and containerized architectures.">
  <div class="resume-page">
    <div class="resume-actions">
      <button class="resume-btn" id="printBtn">Print / Save as PDF</button>
      <a href="/" class="resume-btn resume-btn-secondary">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>

    <div class="resume-sheet" id="resumeSheet">
      <header class="resume-header">
        <div>
          <h1 class="resume-name">Mas Muhammad</h1>
          <div class="resume-role">Senior Backend Engineer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-contact">
          <div><a href="mailto:masmuh@engineer.com" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none">masmuh@engineer.com</a></div>
          <div><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/masmuh" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none">linkedin.com/in/masmuh</a></div>
          <div><a href="https://github.com/masmuh" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none">github.com/masmuh</a></div>
          <div>Indonesia · Open to Remote Worldwide</div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Summary</h2>
        <p class="resume-body">Senior Backend Engineer with 11 years of experience — including 2 years as Technical Lead — specializing in the .NET ecosystem, distributed systems, and containerized backend architectures. Proven track record delivering mission-critical, high-availability systems for multinational clients including Sanofi, Shell, Boston Scientific, Biogen, and Sampoerna. Published author of <em>Mastering .NET 10: Modern Backend Development</em>. Remote-work veteran (8+ years).</p>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Key Achievements</h2>
        <ul class="resume-list">
          <li>Architected backend processing 25,000+ ZIP archives/month across 128 database shards with 67 orchestrated background jobs — zero critical downtime for 4+ years</li>
          <li>Built high-performance SAP middleware for Boston Scientific (DRMS) and Biogen — reducing order-to-ERP cycle from 24 hrs to 5 min, reconciliation errors -90%</li>
          <li>Engineered full SAP ByDesign ERP automation — eliminating ~20 hrs/week of manual data entry</li>
          <li>Led refactor from monolithic legacy codebase to modular .NET Core — reducing deployment cycles from days to hours</li>
          <li>Authored organization-wide Clean Architecture Blueprint — reduced engineer onboarding time by ~50%</li>
          <li>Published <em>Mastering .NET 10: Modern Backend Development</em> on Amazon — covering Cloud-Native patterns, Multi-Tenancy, CQRS, and Kubernetes orchestration</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Experience</h2>

        <div class="resume-job">
          <div class="resume-job-header">
            <div>
              <div class="resume-job-title">Senior Backend Engineer</div>
              <div class="resume-job-company">Kano Solution · Remote</div>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-job-date">Apr 2020 — Present</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="resume-list">
            <li>Architected a custom high-throughput distributed backend managing 67 background jobs and 128 database shards, processing 25,000+ complex archives/month — zero critical downtime for 4+ years</li>
            <li>Authored organization-wide Clean Architecture Blueprint — reduced engineer onboarding time by ~50%, standardized across 3 product teams</li>
            <li>Led team of 3 developers as Technical Lead for Project CRA (Sampoerna) — delivered on-time within 6-month timeline</li>
            <li>Refactored monolithic legacy codebase into modular .NET Core — reducing deployment cycle from days to hours</li>
            <li>Maintained 5+ third-party API integrations (SAP ERP, Xendit, Shipper) across concurrent production systems</li>
            <li>Built Go-based data staging engine for Project Bagong with MongoDB Aggregation and distributed cron orchestration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="resume-job">
          <div class="resume-job-header">
            <div>
              <div class="resume-job-title">Software Engineer</div>
              <div class="resume-job-company">Wiyasa / EACIIT · Remote</div>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-job-date">Oct 2015 — Mar 2020</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="resume-list">
            <li>Solely responsible for architecture, development, and maintenance of backend services for Shell across 3+ regional business units</li>
            <li>Led SAP ByDesign ERP integration — automating critical workflows and eliminating ~20 hrs/week of manual data entry</li>
            <li>Built high-performance SAP middleware for Boston Scientific &amp; Biogen — order-to-ERP: 24 hrs → 5 min, reconciliation errors -90%</li>
            <li>Implemented PCI-compliant Xendit payment flow and Shipper logistics API for live shipment tracking</li>
            <li>Built automated Power BI data pipeline serving 10+ stakeholders with near-real-time dashboards</li>
            <li>SQL Server &amp; MongoDB performance overhaul — query latency -70% under peak transactional loads</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="resume-job">
          <div class="resume-job-header">
            <div>
              <div class="resume-job-title">Technical Lead / Software Engineer</div>
              <div class="resume-job-company">Quantum Leap · Surabaya</div>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-job-date">Nov 2014 — Sep 2015</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="resume-list">
            <li>Delivered custom ERP modules for 4 clients spanning manufacturing and trading sectors</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="resume-job">
          <div class="resume-job-header">
            <div>
              <div class="resume-job-title">Full Stack Developer</div>
              <div class="resume-job-company">Infomedia · Jakarta</div>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-job-date">Jul 2014 — Oct 2014</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="resume-list">
            <li>Solely designed and implemented 4 interconnected business systems for Sanofi (Sales Incentive, Inventory, Registration, Scrap Management)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="resume-job">
          <div class="resume-job-header">
            <div>
              <div class="resume-job-title">Backend Developer</div>
              <div class="resume-job-company">Solusi247 · Jakarta</div>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-job-date">Jun 2013 — Jul 2014</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="resume-list">
            <li>Managed backend services for Telkomsel broadcast system � high-volume SMS gateway processing thousands of messages daily</li>
            <li>Built COMMET middleware (Oracle PL/SQL) for real-time CUG provisioning for millions of MSISDNs</li>
            <li>Engineered Teman Telkomsel (Web-to-SMS Gateway) with AES-256 PII encryption</li>
            <li>Intensive PL/SQL optimization for OLTP/OLAP workloads � reducing report generation time by ~50%</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Tech Stack</h2>
        <div class="resume-skills">
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Languages:</span>
            <span>C#, .NET Core 6/8/10, ASP.NET Core, Go, TypeScript, Oracle PL/SQL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Architecture:</span>
            <span>Clean Architecture, Microservices, CQRS, Event Sourcing, DDD, Multi-Tenancy</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Databases:</span>
            <span>SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Oracle, Redis, InfluxDB, LiteDB</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Infrastructure:</span>
            <span>Docker, Kubernetes/GKE, AWS S3, Nginx, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">AI/ML Tooling:</span>
            <span>Whisper.cpp, OpenRouter LLM API, On-device Inference, Tauri v2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Frontend:</span>
            <span>React.js, Vue.js, Tauri/Wails, .NET MAUI, SignalR</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Integrations:</span>
            <span>SAP ByDesign (OData/SOAP), Xendit (PCI), Shipper, E-Faktur, Bank Mandiri, Power BI</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Frontend:</span>
            <span>React.js, Vue.js, Tauri/Wails, .NET MAUI, SignalR</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Integrations:</span>
            <span>SAP ByDesign (OData/SOAP), Xendit (PCI), Shipper, E-Faktur, Bank Mandiri, Power BI</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-skill-group">
            <span class="resume-skill-cat">Observability:</span>
            <span>Grafana, InfluxDB, NLog, Structured Logging</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Education</h2>
        <ul class="resume-list">
          <li><strong>B.CS (S.Kom)</strong> — Computer Science, Universitas Muhammadiyah Malang. GPA: 3.39 / 4.0. Graduated May 2013.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Languages</h2>
        <ul class="resume-list">
          <li><strong>Bahasa Indonesia</strong> — Native</li>
          <li><strong>English</strong> — Professional Working Proficiency (8+ years daily async collaboration across global teams)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="resume-section">
        <h2 class="resume-section-title">Publication</h2>
        <ul class="resume-list">
          <li><strong>Mastering .NET 10: Modern Backend Development</strong> — Amazon, 2024. Covers Cloud-Native patterns, Multi-Tenancy, CQRS, Event Sourcing, and Kubernetes orchestration.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer class="resume-footer">
        Full portfolio &amp; case studies: <strong><a href="https://masmuh.web.id/portfolio" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none">masmuh.web.id/portfolio</a></strong>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .resume-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 100px 24px 60px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .resume-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .resume-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--bg);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
  }

  .resume-btn:hover {
    background: var(--green);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .resume-btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
    color: var(--cyan);
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
  }

  .resume-btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--cyan-glow);
  }

  .resume-sheet {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 48px;
  }

  .resume-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--cyan);
  }

  .resume-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .resume-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  .resume-contact {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .resume-section {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .resume-section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .resume-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .resume-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .resume-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .resume-list li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .resume-list strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .resume-job {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .resume-job-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .resume-job-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .resume-job-company {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .resume-job-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .resume-skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .resume-skill-group {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .resume-skill-cat {
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .resume-footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .resume-footer strong {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .resume-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .resume-contact {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .resume-job-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .resume-sheet {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .resume-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @page {
    margin: 15mm 18mm;
  }

  @media print {
    html, body {
      background: white !important;
      color: #1a1a1a !important;
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }
    body::before, body::after {
      display: none !important;
    }
    .cursor, .cursor-ring {
      display: none !important;
    }
    nav, .resume-actions, .mobile-overlay, .mobile-nav, .nav-hamburger {
      display: none !important;
    }
    .resume-page {
      padding: 0 !important;
      max-width: none !important;
    }
    .resume-sheet {
      border: none !important;
      background: white !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    .resume-section {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .resume-job {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .resume-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      orphans: 3;
      widows: 3;
    }
    .resume-header {
      page-break-after: avoid;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom-color: #0066cc !important;
    }
    .resume-footer {
      page-break-before: avoid;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 10px;
      border-top-color: #cccccc !important;
    }

    .resume-name {
      color: #0a0a0a !important;
      font-size: 22pt !important;
    }
    .resume-role, .resume-section-title, .resume-skill-cat {
      color: #0066cc !important;
    }
    .resume-contact, .resume-body, .resume-list li, .resume-skill-group {
      color: #333333 !important;
    }
    .resume-body {
      font-size: 9.5pt !important;
      line-height: 1.4 !important;
    }
    .resume-job-title {
      color: #0a0a0a !important;
      font-size: 12pt !important;
    }
    .resume-job-company {
      color: #0066cc !important;
      font-size: 9pt !important;
    }
    .resume-job-date {
      font-size: 8pt !important;
    }
    .resume-section-title {
      font-size: 9pt !important;
      margin-bottom: 6px !important;
      padding-bottom: 4px !important;
      border-bottom-color: #cccccc !important;
    }
    .resume-list li {
      font-size: 9.5pt !important;
      line-height: 1.35 !important;
      padding-left: 12px !important;
    }
    .resume-list li::before {
      color: #0066cc !important;
      font-size: 8px !important;
    }
    .resume-list strong {
      color: #0a0a0a !important;
    }
    .resume-skills {
      gap: 3px !important;
    }
    .resume-skill-group {
      font-size: 9pt !important;
      line-height: 1.4 !important;
    }
    .resume-footer {
      font-size: 9pt !important;
    }
    .resume-footer strong {
      color: #0066cc !important;
    }
    .resume-btn, .resume-btn-secondary {
      display: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('printBtn')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
    window.print();
  });
</script>